title: Cruising World - August 2014  USA
description:
Cruising World - August 2014  USA

116 Pages | True PDF | English | 28 MB 


This magazine is edited for those who enjoy cruising and are interested in acquiring new skills enabling them to navigate and sail safely in coastal waters, on lakes and across oceans. About half of the articles involve information and techniques aimed at helping an owner maintain and enjoy their sailboat, while the other half reflect reader experiences.
